0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:23:00.000Z","msg":"平時叫女友做多D運動强身健體"},{"pid":"7f8d910fdcf2eceaaa13b9bad8940be77af55b05","tid":293412,"uid":5088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:24:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真，趁佢無事果又傾下，我地傾左3年佢開始明白同埋努力唔發咁多脾氣<br />\n但都要果幾日前後小心中地雷，盡量唔好俾佢處於啲太辛苦既狀態，熱呀攰呀果啲<br />\n已經兩個月冇出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁啱去緊旅行先嚟m<br />\n邊有可能唔熱唔攰<br />\n我已經攞晒啲行李又成日引佢笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁無計啦，硬食啦<br />\nI know that feel bros<br />\n同埋我女朋友有時發脾氣係包含左嬲緊自己點解要咁，你試下你女朋友會唔會都有呢個感覺，如果你講中左佢會好過啲冇咁大脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a631bd35366db9f75db51d5208179ea41442ba","tid":293412,"uid":6542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:25:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真，趁佢無事果又傾下，我地傾左3年佢開始明白同埋努力唔發咁多脾氣<br />\n但都要果幾日前後小心中地雷，盡量唔好俾佢處於啲太辛苦既狀態，熱呀攰呀果啲<br />\n已經兩個月冇出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁啱去緊旅行先嚟m<br />\n邊有可能唔熱唔攰<br />\n我已經攞晒啲行李又成日引佢笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n盡左力都比人爆嗰下先辛苦"},{"pid":"e838cc8e66820a75d2920a74b9505c56e0ee1977","tid":293412,"uid":799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:26:41.000Z","msg":"黎M果時盡量唔掂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a924f91f9358da14865628b286655c5d13fe02","tid":293412,"uid":6542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:27:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分手咪得囉，咁簡單都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n除左有時發下脾氣之外女朋友對我好好<br />\n又唔會同啲厹傾計<br />\n我唔想分手呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d73934d875f0594cbed07dfd13d1fad2a60ad76","tid":293412,"uid":81762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:27:57.000Z","msg":"諗方法令佢唔痛<br />\n未係佢開口前已經關心佢<br />\n喂佢飲暖水、比糖佢食，表現心痛佢<br />\n做出黎，唔係叫佢飲水叫佢食野<br />\n再陰公b陰公b叫幾日<br />\n比平時更關心、包容<br />\n<br />\n唔知你女朋友受唔受<br />\n我受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算想發脾氣都唔想搞到佢"},{"pid":"9bfd406634e894cb6c6956a7f7675e2d87516302","tid":293412,"uid":6542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:29:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時叫女友做多D運動强身健體</blockquote><br />\n有咩運動可以減緩m痛？"},{"pid":"7859add31898bf08de368c596ca9ed18923ff20f","tid":293412,"uid":56912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:31:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真，趁佢無事果又傾下，我地傾左3年佢開始明白同埋努力唔發咁多脾氣<br />\n但都要果幾日前後小心中地雷，盡量唔好俾佢處於啲太辛苦既狀態，熱呀攰呀果啲<br />\n已經兩個月冇出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁啱去緊旅行先嚟m<br />\n邊有可能唔熱唔攰<br />\n我已經攞晒啲行李又成日引佢笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知你地去邊度旅行啦<br />\n但都要試下轉啲無咁辛苦既行程<br />\n定時定侯放佢去廁所<br />\n天氣熱又唔飲得凍野，成身汗下面又濕又焗真係好難頂"},{"pid":"8365a56003099bb733829d4d58845f43e797c7d6","tid":293412,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:31:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平時叫女友做多D運動强身健體</blockquote><br />\n有咩運動可以減緩m痛？</blockquote><br />\n其實運動開既人小m痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"811ffea51de5b46cfe01c7aa447891d5ee356dac","tid":293412,"uid":122514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:32:56.000Z","msg":"之前見日本藥妝有隻止PMS症狀嘅藥, 講到差唔多嚟M嘅症狀都醫到, 即係頭痛,情緒不穩, 煩躁不安個d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 非打手, 無買到"},{"pid":"242a906357ea37a